item.title: CVE-2021-20719|2024-08-03T17:53:21.782Z -- nippon%20antenna%20co.%2Cltd. -- rfntps
item.description: RFNTPS firmware versions System_01000004 and earlier, and Web_01000004 and earlier allow an attacker on the same network segment to execute arbitrary OS commands with a root privilege via unspecified vectors.
